<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Pliney Fisk</author>
<hymn_number>89</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nitak nanta fehna kak o̱,
 Ʋba yakni yoka
 Ont chukowʋt, Chisʋs fehna
 Ont pisa la chi̱ cho?

[V2]
 Yakni 'lʋppa aiahanta
 Ik pim iksho hocha,
 Ai ilbʋshʋt pilli hoke;
 Pi̱ Mi̱ko Chisʋs ma!

[V3]
 Shilombish Holitopa ya̱
 Et ish pimakbano,
 Ahnit himak nitak oka
 E chim asilhhʋshke.

[V4]
 Chiso ik pi ahoboshke;
 Anumpa ilbʋsha
 Himak nitak fehna hoka
 Pit e chihi̱mʋshke.

[V5]
 Pit e chim asihi̱hla ka
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke:
 Chihowa holitopa ma!
 Auet ish haklashke.

[V6]
 Nan il ayoshoba puta
 Ish pi̱ kashoffashke;
 Shilombish Holitopa ya̱
 E chim asilhhʋshke.</lyrics>
<title>Nitak nanta fehna kak o ƲIT89</title>
</song>